#my_beliefs.col-md-12
	.beliefs_button_container
		.belief-images
			.belief-image-button.blue-link{"data-name" => "Travel can be used as a force for good.", "data-description" => "In addition to being the world's largest wealth distribution mechanism, travel can widen perspectives, evoke empathy and bring our world closer together. Travel has not only exposed the beauty and excitement in life but also, how unaware many are about one another. Because of this, I’ve dedicated my life helping others experience our world in a meaningful and positive way.", style: "background: url('#{asset_path("background/ExperienceDesign.jpg")}') center center no-repeat; border-bottom: 4px solid #F4D03F;"}
