			.belief-image-button.green-link{"data-name" => "Offline travel experiences begin online.", "data-description" => "From discovery to post-trip, I’ve developed a particular interest in how travel experiences develop online from the perspective of both the traveler and the service providers. For the past three years, I've been working with hundreds of tour operators and guides with the most authentic travel experiences to determine how best we can bridge their offline offerings on to the web.", style: "background: url('#{asset_path("background/adventureconsulting.jpeg")}') center center no-repeat"}
				Digital Travel.
			.belief-image-button.yellow-link{"data-name" => "Entrepreneurship can solve our biggest challenges.", "data-description" => "Not only do I love problem solving, I have a healthy obsession with defining the right problems to solve through design thinking and empathy research (largely due to my experiences with Stanford’s d.school and Unreasonable at Sea). When I can pinpoint a problem worth solving as well as connect with users and their needs, I develop businesses around problems, not solutions.", style: "background: url('#{asset_path("background/Quinnlocal.jpg")}') center center no-repeat"}
				Entrepreneurship.
